 This is the first time, readers of Auto Bild allrad voted the Wrangler not just as their favourite import, but overall as the best in its category, beating all models from premium brand German manufacturers. The result underlines the appeal the Wrangler – the true descendant of the Willys-Overland MB, the world’s first light-weight 4×4 vehicle – continues to hold for off-roading and SUV enthusiasts and the value they place on authenticity and uniqueness. The Auto Bild allrad poll is conducted annually and this year a total of 218 models featured across 10 categories. ALSO READ: May 2020 sales show fractional improvement